{"tid":513192,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"不如仿效Reddit，整番個\"Change my view\" post","createTime":"2017-12-29T09:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T11:59:00.000Z","uid":138409,"like":116,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f1949e71331d6c8cf1e4895346590be5a95932cc","tid":513192,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:32:36.000Z","msg":"話說之前見到Reddit有個subreddit叫&ldquo;Change my view&rdquo;<br />\n(<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/changemyview/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fchangemyview%2F&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0Yvedr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=fbd73c00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com/r/changemyview/</a>)<br />\n目的係鼓勵人挑戰自己的成見，簡單而言就是自願被人圍攻。<br />\n<br />\n最近學術台有個po 講女權運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，亦有觸及賣淫問題，我就以此為例。<br />\n<br />\n以下呢位仁兄提倡賣淫合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/29/172136_ca3fdf610321841e0808baf5a00ea376.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F29%2F172136_ca3fdf610321841e0808baf5a00ea376.png&h=88b208bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就有不同人反駁並且嘗試說服他 放棄原有的想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/29/172602_02796f2a9346d8d668f14ef93f96c24d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F29%2F172602_02796f2a9346d8d668f14ef93f96c24d.png&h=e69e6e8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/29/172604_42e91b29d75392c424aba995aea6fada.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F29%2F172604_42e91b29d75392c424aba995aea6fada.png&h=9e647e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要係整個討論過程的目標不是單純辯駁，而是樓主要願意改變自己想法。樓主可以比一個&ldquo;Delta&rdquo;比成功改變樓主自己想法的人，以作鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得最有意思的是，這種設計令討論不會陷入圍爐取暖。相對一般po都有所謂「回聲谷效應」／「同溫層」的弊病，&ldquo;Change my view&rdquo;能帶來更有意思的討論"},{"pid":"b0adfbda5ddd7a9a92ebfa1549f17bb0303084cf","tid":513192,"uid":63,"like":171,"dislike":1,"score":170,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:38:57.000Z","msg":"賤種華人最後只會演變成各持己見 潑婦罵街<br />\n遑論依個學生論壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2eaf1405a6e0ec1926986be28999f8ec9681d8","tid":513192,"uid":76098,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"有意思 但唔睇好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終呢到仲停留係罐頭式討論 難d好似外國論壇咁"},{"pid":"022288aca020decefbe715c2a23c05297d82b81c","tid":513192,"uid":138409,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"我又覺得不用那麼灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終學術台不時都會有高汁po，我對學術台仍然有信心。<br />\n不過&ldquo;Change my view&rdquo;可以運作，重點在於reddit有管理員（moderator）制度，如果有留言違反版規（例如講粗口、人身攻擊之類）可以將之移除。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以能否引入&ldquo;Change my view&rdquo;模式，我覺得問題在於如何確保管理員不會濫權，降低討論者的戒心。"},{"pid":"48cce7c62e7ab2e80612cc66637ab8e684b6a651","tid":513192,"uid":90863,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:00:29.000Z","msg":"最重要係整個討論過程的目標不是單純辯駁，而是樓主要願意改變自己想法。<br />\n<br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"3f91574b784a3ddf2c50c40de6bb858a6fa7ccd7","tid":513192,"uid":517,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"等睇耶撚煙撚開post 被人屌到開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fecd44e9c8f84f5f7e4591bb840af712715ef45","tid":513192,"uid":76098,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"3f91574b784a3ddf2c50c40de6bb858a6fa7ccd7","tid":513192,"uid":517,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"等睇耶撚煙撚開post 被人屌到開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:14:24.000Z","msg":"呢個都係問題<br />\nd post會唔會黎黎去去幾督屁 淨係圍繞特定宗教政治issue 冇d新意呢<br />\n又或者有人專登開po博屌<br />\n<br />\n始終對香港forum冇咩信心 唔講討論質素 淨係d topic, 鬼佬d創意都多元化10倍 <br />\n老土講句 香港太壓抑 創意都被現實綁住"},{"pid":"a29724b241368544aebeb24befc55f068edb3ed3","tid":513192,"uid":55488,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a73b97cdaba4f7da186c79edc46a515b616fd34","tid":513192,"uid":76098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"022288aca020decefbe715c2a23c05297d82b81c","tid":513192,"uid":138409,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"我又覺得不用那麼灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終學術台不時都會有高汁po，我對學術台仍然有信心。<br />\n不過&ldquo;Change my view&rdquo;可以運作，重點在於reddit有管理員（moderator）制度，如果有留言違反版規（例如講粗口、人身攻擊之類）可以將之移除。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以能否引入&ldquo;Change my view&rdquo;模式，我覺得問題在於如何確保管理員不會濫權，降低討論者的戒心。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"做分區好d 可以gp埋方便睇<br />\n其實好多subreddit都好有趣有意思，e.g. showerthoughts 但好難將佢地個套搬黎連登 我地分區太籠統 可能唔夠多人 好難再分細區 <br />\n至於管理員，比起稱唔稱職，連登肯俾錢請人做先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abfa831300b653b40b5d0ea26e1b6b3e8823814","tid":513192,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"去睇下cc台<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9bf20e5cfc8d05a59458707871d7da18e12198","tid":513192,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:32:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ace5f174aa165409a3cec337bd6b81eb456c8629","tid":513192,"uid":138409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8abfa831300b653b40b5d0ea26e1b6b3e8823814","tid":513192,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"去睇下cc台<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"所以我強調 版規 同 管理員制度 很重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7f14170eb1c5e755264f2a72ea764a4f2d1875","tid":513192,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a73b97cdaba4f7da186c79edc46a515b616fd34","tid":513192,"uid":76098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"022288aca020decefbe715c2a23c05297d82b81c","tid":513192,"uid":138409,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"我又覺得不用那麼灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終學術台不時都會有高汁po，我對學術台仍然有信心。<br />\n不過&ldquo;Change my view&rdquo;可以運作，重點在於reddit有管理員（moderator）制度，如果有留言違反版規（例如講粗口、人身攻擊之類）可以將之移除。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以能否引入&ldquo;Change my view&rdquo;模式，我覺得問題在於如何確保管理員不會濫權，降低討論者的戒心。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"做分區好d 可以gp埋方便睇<br />\n其實好多subreddit都好有趣有意思，e.g. showerthoughts 但好難將佢地個套搬黎連登 我地分區太籠統 可能唔夠多人 好難再分細區 <br />\n至於管理員，比起稱唔稱職，連登肯俾錢請人做先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"其實Reddit的設計比較特別，基本上人人都可以開台（我懷疑百度貼吧就係抄Reddit<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n我在想可不可以在學術台之下開一個sub-台<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又或者引入tag功能，方便分類<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">#changemyview</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78811375fad87c05fde42a7b594f063357176c49","tid":513192,"uid":134774,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5f9bf20e5cfc8d05a59458707871d7da18e12198","tid":513192,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:32:26