2-29T13:18:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=67OtrDCurSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D67OtrDCurSw&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0Yvedr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=21141365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=67OtrDCurSw</a><br />\nBill Burr講得好好 直接打壓班人根本冇用 要教化<br />\n理念完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"不過如果係用教化的態度去面對異議者，人地可能會覺得你很condescending<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而更難溝通<br />\n所以 我認為 #changemyview 講求一種「即使我極不認同你的意見，仍將你視為可理性溝通交流的<span style=\"color: red;\">平等</span>個體」的精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsorry for 左膠feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:30:12.000Z","msg":"佢老婆好似好撚唔gur佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個口水佬開起聖人mode講野又幾make sense, 炒人只係showing how powerful the group is,對個人完全冇幫助<br />\n連登呢個論壇係議題正反面好似打仗咁一係你死一係我亡唔會有changemyview呢樣野"},{"pid":"4ad65dbacd561f234a839ceb0393ca0e3dcff64f","tid":513192,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:32:27.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得可以初步試下這樣：<br />\n如果有人真心想理性討論，有心理準備改變自己立場，<br />\n開po時就在標題以 <span style=\"color: blue;\">#changemyview</span>為開頭，<br />\n這樣各位巴絲就算不同意樓主意見，都嘗試平心靜氣去與他／她討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然我知道靠人自律就無咩可能做到，這個提議都相當天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係路係人行出來，在配套未完善前，試下無妨。<br />\n<br />\nbtw 我所指的「平心靜氣」，係真係連粗口／諷刺／挑釁都禁止<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為如果你想說服人，無可能係屌番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講講下，一句「屌你老母」，全部人起哂剛，討論都好難維持下去<br />\n所以就算你話我道德L都好啦，我覺得呢點一定要堅持，要不然#changemyview就無意思<br />\n<br />\n細節參閱reddit #changemyview 版規<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/changemyview/wiki/rules#wiki_rule_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fchangemyview%2Fwiki%2Frules%23wiki_rule_2&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0Yvedr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=818539da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com/r/changemyview/wiki/rules#wiki_rule_2</a><br />\n<br />\n以下引用部分版規原文：<br />\n<br />\nRule 2<br />\n&quot;Don't be rude or hostile to other users. Your comment will be removed even if the rest of it is solid.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Would you walk into a hospital and slap the patients because they're sick? Would you enter an Alcoholics Anonymous meeting and call everyone a worthless drunk? Would you enter a barber shop, point at the line of customers waiting for a haircut, and call them dirty long-haired hippies?</span><br />\n<br />\nImagine if there was a place, somewhere, that a person with an unpopular view could go to learn about the other side of issue, to try and understand different perspectives, and do so without fear of being shamed. This subreddit is intended to be that place. <span style=\"color: red;\">If you think that a person's opinion is vile, and you're insulting them in Change My View, then you're being unproductive. This is meant to be a place where even the most unpopular views can come to work it out.</span> (Here's some more info on controversial threads).<br />\n<br />\nA very common reason that comments are removed is implying or stating that someone &quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">lacks reading comprehension</span>&quot; (or is failing to use it). To be clear, this (and other forms of passive or active condescension) are prohibited by Rule 2.<br />\n<br />\nWe are somewhat more flexible about rudeness towards someone's argument rather than their character. However, don't use narrow semantic distinctions to try to dodge Rule 2. <span style=\"color: red;\">Calling an argument &quot;moronic&quot; is effectively calling the person making it a moron</span>, in part because arguments themselves don't have intelligence, and therefore can't even be &quot;moronic&quot;... only the arguer can be. An argument can be called fallacious or incorrect, but it can't be called stupid.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Variations of rude comments like &quot;If you don't agree with me you are stupid&quot; or &quot;Only a retard would voice an opinion like yours.&quot; will be counted as rule 2 violations.</span> Constructing a hypothetical argument where they have to agree with you or be bad is against the spirit of changemyview. Different perspectives should be celebrated, and if those perspectives are wrong they should be challenged on factual grounds not with attacks on people as personal attacks tend to lead to people shutting down."},{"pid":"ff79611ee84b6d05f146453ce43835b3ebb70af9","tid":513192,"uid":30831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e9b22371d9f2378b5faa78312e58e19c40c4a99","tid":513192,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76b6c4d3fa52d1cda60cc5ea9a38712c4334a191","tid":513192,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:18:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=67OtrDCurSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D67OtrDCurSw&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0Yvedr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=21141365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=67OtrDCurSw</a><br />\nBill Burr講得好好 直接打壓班人根本冇用 要教化<br />\n理念完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"不過如果係用教化的態度去面對異議者，人地可能會覺得你很condescending<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而更難溝通<br />\n所以 我認為 #changemyview 講求一種「即使我極不認同你的意見，仍將你視為可理性溝通交流的<span style=\"color: red;\">平等</span>個體」的精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsorry for 左膠feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:38:09.000Z","msg":"你岩 教化個詞用得唔好 自膠<br />\nBill個意思就係同你一樣 平等個體 同對方坐底慢慢傾"},{"pid":"3c6825840ce95bec71209176376a5cd938946126","tid":513192,"uid":62950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2cf8ab1b6b6d4857a6df9421b694aeb8d14d8a0","tid":513192,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"098c067b24ee6f28b4669059d2790920160963de","tid":513192,"uid":13885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:08:04.000Z","msg":"其實有得搞 但點去處理5毛洗版問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"都係哥句，如何建立一個具公信力的管理員制度是重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:39:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得無可能搞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登始終係由舊(紅)登 copy個模式過黎<br />\n<br />\n你宜家要係連登呢個生態環境下 加入管理員同 以前笑富有中國特式既共產主義一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再者<br />\n連登學術post就算間中有 有質素既post都好啦<br />\n只要間中有 錯別字 疑似蝗字 簡化字等都會變左潑婦罵街<br />\n<br />\n而連登會員本身個自律程度又唔高 <br />\n你睇風post氣候post就知 明明佢自己入學術台 但唔係討論學術仲好似大爺咁問你 幾時掛八號etc<br />\n你答佢又死 屌佢又死  <br />\n有管理員 當你封佢留言仲死 佢實去返其他台批鬥你 <br />\n再係其他台吹大雞質疑管理員既立場目的 同成個管理員制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e27b3bf4d9a3d235dc023c3a2eec0021fbe0cbd","tid":513192,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5872ed132094ebde6eb00c9faf5cc3817685fb53","tid":513192,"uid":93890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ef66188966f6de387ae0c17b91d4bc5255943f3","tid":513192,"uid":76098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"45a1cbd9f1f423b6fb8609ebd540359002977f9e","tid":513192,"uid":93890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T11:39:43.000Z","msg":"堅守信念既點都唔會比你說服到<br />\n正如你同你藍絲廢老講中國幾衰 佢地都會無視<br />\n<br />